sequenceDiagram
    participant Service as Internal service
    participant API as FastAPI API
    participant Auth as authentik OIDC/JWKS
    participant Handler as Protected route

    Service->>API: Request with Authorization bearer token
    alt Internal service token
        API->>API: Compare with configured AUTH_SERVICE_TOKEN
        API->>Handler: Treat as service principal
    else OIDC access token
        API->>Auth: Fetch/cache JWKS when needed
        API->>API: Verify signature, issuer, audience, expiry
        API->>API: Map groups/claims to roles
        API->>Handler: Treat as external client principal
    else Missing or invalid token
        API-->>Service: 401 unauthorized or 403 forbidden
    end
